    """ Time Consuming """

3.85 s ¬± 44.5 ms per loop (mean ¬± std. dev. of 7 runs, 1 loop each)

>>> for i in range(10000):
>>>     for j in range(10000):
>>>         t.append(i*j)

""" Memory Consuming """
